data.description: Up to $10,000 in concession to Buyer, Why wait on a new build. 4 Bedroom 2 bath single level home was built late 2022. Open floor plan with large great room. Beautiful kitchen features upgraded cabinets, quartz counter tops, stainless appliance and sink. custom island, soft close doors and drawers. there is a super Pantry. (could be opened to make a great office) Spacious Primary bedroom with ensuite and large walk in closet. Beautifully landscaped back yard with turf and pavers already installed. upgraded tile in all areas except the bedrooms. Close to ALA charter school. Solar installed with a battery back up system. never lose power to be assumed by buyer. Premium lot (15K) that back up to park. Great neighborhood, close to shopping and freeway. This home is a must see
